parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality to the occupants, compromising their safety.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
despite the severity of the impact
potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended airbag deployment can cause distraction, loss of control, and accidents, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbags deploy unexpectedly
without a crash or significant impact
potentially causing the driver to lose control of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Intermittent Brake Failure and ABS/Tracton Control Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent brake failure and illumination of ABS and traction control warning lights can cause a loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The brakes momentarily lock
the airbag light illuminates on the dashboard
the ABS and traction control lights illuminate on the dashboard
the brakes appear to work normally but warning lights are present.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fracture of the camshaft chain guides can lead to catastrophic engine failure, resulting in costly repairs or even requiring the vehicle to be junked.
symptoms: Plastic and metal shavings observed in the lower oil pan
jump in timing
engine failure
and potentially catastrophic consequences.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sidewall Blowout in Kuhmo Z-Rated Tires
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A sudden sidewall blowout can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Sidewall blowout without any external damage
sudden loss of air pressure
loud noise
and vibration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic transmission can cause the vehicle to slip or hesitate when shifting gears, leading to loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the transmission leaks fluid
the vehicle experiences difficulty shifting into gear
the vehicle experiences sudden loss of power
the vehicle's engine RPMs fluctuate erratically.
